# Audit pipeline

- **Global editable sources:** `docs/audit/raw-data.json`, `docs/audit/teams-mapping.yaml`, `docs/audit/rules/*.yaml`.
- **Do not hand-edit** `docs/audit/runs/*/input/**` after a run; those are **frozen snapshots**. Change globals and re-run.
- **Scripts:** `npm run audit:fetch`, `npm run audit:run` (optional `--max-repos N`).
- **Outputs per run:** `runs/<id>/output/summary.md`, `emeritus-candidates.md`, `full-report.json`.
- **Spec Kit:** see `spec/audit/constitution.md` and https://github.com/github/spec-kit
